snippet.title: Gangsta Bean 2 Playthrough (Easy - No Commentary)
snippet.description:
A Casual Playthrough of LeafWorthy Entertainment's Gangsta Bean 2 on Easy Mode. Just a neat flash game from when I was younger that I wanted to play. Played on flashpoint. On a separate note I am gonna have to work on making less cringe thumbnails lol.

LeafWorthy: 
https://leafworthy.com/
(The dude is seriously awesome, check him out)
His Twitter:
https://twitter.com/leafworthy

Flashpoint: https://bluemaxima.org/flashpoint/
